  <brief_title>Combination Therapy of Hydroxyurea With L-Carnitine and Magnesium Chloride in Thalassemia Intermedia</brief_title>
  <official_title>The Effect of Combination Therapy of Hydroxyurea With L- Carnitine and Magnesium Chloride on he-Matologic Parameters and Cardiac Function of β-Thalassemia Intermedia Patients.</official_title>
  <sponsors>
    <lead_sponsor>
