    <has_dmc>Yes</has_dmc>
  </oversight_info>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is determination of the efficacy of combination of hydroxyurea with
      L-carnitine or magnesium in improving hematologic parameters and cardiac status in patients
      with β-thalassemia intermedia in comparison with hydroxyurea alone .
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
